est_patch": "", "problem_statement": "Sphinx docstring issues\nTODO for another time:\r\n```\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/commands/core.py:docstring of discord.SlashCommand.cog:1: WARNING: duplicate object description of discord.SlashCommand.cog, other instance in api/application_commands, use :no-index: for one of them\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/bot.py:docstring of discord.client.Client.get_all_channels:8: WARNING: Literal block ends without a blank line; unexpected unindent. [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/client.py:docstring of discord.client.Client.get_all_channels:8: WARNING: Literal block ends without a blank line; unexpected unindent. [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/automod.py:docstring of discord.automod.AutoModTriggerMetadata:72: WARNING: Duplicate explicit target name: \"here\". [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/raw_models.py:docstring of discord.raw_models.RawTypingEvent:45: WARNING: Duplicate explicit target name: \"gateway\". [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/raw_models.py:docstring of discord.raw_models.RawMessageDeleteEvent:37: WARNING: Duplicate explicit target name: \"gateway\". [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/raw_models.py:docstring of discord.raw_models.RawBulkMessageDeleteEvent:37: WARNING: Duplicate explicit target name: \"gateway\". [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/raw_models.py:docstring of discord.raw_models.RawMessageUpdateEvent:40: WARNING: Duplicate explicit target name: \"gateway\". [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/raw_models.py:docstring of discord.raw_models.RawReactionActionEvent:91: WARNING: Duplicate explicit target name: \"gateway\". [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/discord/raw_models.py:docstring of discord.raw_models.RawReactionClearEvent:31: WARNING: Duplicate explicit target name: \"gateway\". [docutils]\r\n/home/runner/work/pycord/pycord/di